    <caseIntroduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Between 2015-2022 renewable energy capacity increased to 125 GW (30%) from 45 GW (15%).</p>
<p>Solar capacity increased from 6 GW to 60 GW. [1]</p>]]></Value>
    </caseIntroduction>
